itle","text":"社会宝践是检彩或现唱标装代贝","index":6,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"2eaca4ac8b"},{"id":"9246ce7d03","type":"paragraph","text":"这是一条适应类帝围庄义全球战略的路接。路。这不是保卫世界和平的道路，而是助长战等危险导我战登的道","index":7,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"2eaca4ac8b"},{"id":"e3aaba624b","type":"paragraph","text":"目前的世界，已经远不是第二次世界大战精夕的世界了。现在","index":8,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"2eaca4ac8b"},{"id":"3e66ccfe83","type":"paragraph","text":"已经有了一个药大的社会主义障营。亚洲、排洲和拉丁美洲的民族","index":9,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"2eaca4ac8b"},{"id":"9da16098a2","type":"paragraph","text":"解放运动风起去涌。世界人民的觉悟已经大大提高。世界革命人民的力量已经大大增强。苏联人民、社主义各国人民、世界各国人","index":10,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"2eaca4ac8b"},{"id":"44737756e2","type":"paragraph","text":"民，绝不能听凭帝国主义战争势力利他们的吹鼓手的支配自己的命","index":11,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"2eaca4ac8b"},{"id":"09976bb984","type":"subtitle","text":"世界云民，网","index":12,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"2eaca4ac8b"},{"id":"294cbc5852","type":"paragraph","text":"运。帝国主义和各国反动派的使啦和战单行为，正在教育人民还步","index":13,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"2eaca4ac8b"},{"id":"59c8b454c6","type":"paragraph","text":"悟起来。那些在战争与和平同题的认上有婚娱点的人，在帝","index":14,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"2eaca4ac8b"},{"id":"c465fd0b2d","type":"subtitle","text":"图主义和反动派的反面教育之下，限多人会吸变过来。对此，我们开子确生。大的","index":15,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"2eaca4ac8b"},{"id":"d8fc808025","type":"paragraph","text":"我们相信，全世界共产党人，全世界人民识要能烤拆穿帝","index":16,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"2eaca4ac8b"},{"id":"e18fb6ffde","type":"paragraph","text":"国主义的局，破修正主义的说言，把维护世界和平的担子担当","index":17,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"2eaca4ac8b"},{"id":"dc211a82db","type":"paragraph","text":"起来，就一定能约粉碎帝图主义发动新的世界大战的计划，保卫住","index":18,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"2eaca4ac8b"},{"id":"72b38a0cbf","type":"paragraph","text":"世界和平。","index":19,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"2eaca4ac8b"},{"id":"afa10a1472","type":"paragraph","te